tibet has recently reopened for cross-border trade. for now though, the crossing is not open to tourists, and special permits are required to visit from either side. myanmar (burma)[edit] entering china from myanmar is possible at the ruili (china)-lashio (myanmar) border crossing, but permits need to be obtained from the burmese authorities in advance. generally, this would require you to join a guided tour. vietnam[edit] for most travelers hanoi is the origin for any overland journey to china. there are currently three international crossings: dong dang (v) - pingxiang (c) you can catch a local bus from hanoi's eastern bus 